the skits with the rollers generally featured cameos by characters from other sid and marty krofft shows , including enik and the sleestak from land of the lost , various characters from h.r. pufnstuf , and dr. shrinker ( now renamed dr. deathray ) and his assistant hugo ( now renamed otto ) .

sid & marty krofft tv : in 1978 this scottish band hosted the krofft superstar hour on s - a-t-u-r-d-a-y nights

the bay city rollers